<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About - Student Attendance Management System (SAMS)</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #f8fafc;
      background-image: 
        radial-gradient(at 0% 0%, rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.02) 0px, transparent 50%),
        radial-gradient(at 100% 100%, rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.01) 0px, transparent 50%);
      background-attachment: fixed;
      color: #334155;
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    /* Executive Typography & Branding */
    .section-title-premium {
      color: #0f172a;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    }
    
    .accent-gradient-bar {
      width: 50px;
      height: 4px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #2563eb 0%, #3b82f6 100%);
      border-radius: 4px;
    }

    /* Ultra-Sleek Container Frameworks */
    .premium-about-card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.8) !important;
      border-radius: 24px !important;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.02), 0 2px 4px -1px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.01);
      transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
    }
    .premium-about-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      background: #ffffff;
      border-color: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.25) !important;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.04) !important;
    }

    /* Functional Core Highlight Enclosures */
    .feature-item-pill {
      background: #f8fafc;
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 14px 18px;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #334155;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .feature-item-pill:hover {
      background: #ffffff;
      border-color: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.3);
      color: #2563eb;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.05);
    }

    /* Minimalist Metrics Matrix View */
    .metric-row {
      border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
      transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
    }
    .metric-row:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
    .metric-row:hover {
      background-color: #fafafa;
    }

    /* Roadmap Node Architecture */
    .roadmap-node {
      background: #f8fafc;
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 28px 22px;
      height: 100%;
      transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
    }
    .roadmap-node:hover {
      background: #ffffff;
      border-color: #2563eb;
      box-shadow: 0 16px 32px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.05);
      transform: translateY(-4px);
    }
    .roadmap-icon-wrap {
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
      background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.06);
      color: #2563eb;
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    /* Custom Checkmark Vector List */
    .checkmark-list-icon {
      width: 20px;
      height: 20px;
      background-color: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.1);
      color: #16a34a;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      margin-top: 3px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    
    .premium-badge {
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-weight: 700;
      padding: 6px 14px;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .tracking-wider-custom {
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <%- include("partials/header") %>

  <main class="container my-5 py-3" style="max-width: 1140px;">
    
    <div class="text-center mb-5 animate__animated animate__fadeIn">
      <span class="badge bg-primary bg-opacity-10 text-primary premium-badge mb-2">Institutional Project Brief</span>
      <h1 class="display-6 section-title-premium mb-3">About SAMS Operations</h1>
      <p class="text-muted mx-auto fs-6 lh-lg" style="max-width: 780px;">
        Student Attendance Management System (SAMS) represents a real-time, contact-free administrative solution developed to replace traditional, error-prone attendance pipelines at UCET, Vinoba Bhave University.
      </p>
      <div class="accent-gradient-bar mx-auto mt-4"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="row g-4 mb-5">
      
      <div class="col-md-7">
        <div class="card h-100 premium-about-card p-4 p-md-5">
          <h2 class="h6 fw-extrabold text-dark text-uppercase tracking-wider-custom mb-3">Project Motivation & Objectives</h2>
          <p class="text-secondary small mb-4 lh-lg">
            Conventional classroom management procedures consume significant segments of instructional hours, introduce high data processing delays, and suffer from proxy attendance liabilities. SAMS systematically restructures student monitoring by targets built directly into the system workflow:
          </p>
          
          <div class="d-flex flex-column gap-3 mb-5">
            <div class="d-flex align-items-start gap-3">
              <div class="checkmark-list-icon">✓</div>
              <p class="small text-secondary mb-0"><strong class="text-dark">Eliminate Proxy Attendance Vulnerabilities:</strong> Eradicates fraudulent record manipulation by utilizing precise facial structural extraction loops to ensure verification integrity.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="d-flex align-items-start gap-3">
              <div class="checkmark-list-icon">✓</div>
              <p class="small text-secondary mb-0"><strong class="text-dark">Maximize Class Time Efficiency:</strong> Transforms the long administrative delay lines of manual rolls into an instantaneous, split-second ambient hardware check-in sequence.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="d-flex align-items-start gap-3">
              <div class="checkmark-list-icon">✓</div>
              <p class="small text-secondary mb-0"><strong class="text-dark">Data-Driven Academic Insights:</strong> Translates raw check-in telemetries into immediate, interactive dashboard percentage figures to effectively track student classroom consistency.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h2 class="h6 fw-extrabold text-dark text-uppercase tracking-wider-custom mb-3">Operational Milestones Achieved</h2>
          <div class="row g-3">
            <div class="col-sm-6">
              <div class="feature-item-pill">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-bolt text-primary small"></i> Processing Under 2 Seconds
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6">
              <div class="feature-item-pill">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-bullseye text-primary small"></i> High Precision Target Threshold
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6">
              <div class="feature-item-pill">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-nodes text-primary small"></i> Continuous Duplicate Filter
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6">
              <div class="feature-item-pill">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-user-lock text-primary small"></i> Localized Verification Privacy
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-5">
        <div class="card h-100 premium-about-card p-4 p-md-5">
          <h2 class="h6 fw-extrabold text-dark text-uppercase tracking-wider-custom mb-4">Functional Requirements Matrix</h2>
          
          <div class="table-responsive my-auto">
            <table class="table table-borderless align-middle m-0">
              <tbody>
                <tr class="metric-row">
                  <td class="py-3 ps-0" style="width: 35%;">
                    <span class="d-block fw-bold text-dark small mb-0">System Roster</span>
                  </td>
                  <td class="pe-0 text-end">
                    <span class="text-muted small">Full student profiles configuration featuring integrated custom image payload parsing optimization.</span>
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="metric-row">
                  <td class="py-3 ps-0">
                    <span class="d-block fw-bold text-dark small mb-0">Biometric Intercept</span>
                  </td>
                  <td class="pe-0 text-end">
                    <span class="text-muted small">Real-time webcam video stream coordinate scanning integrated with active multi-record log compilation prevention.</span>
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="metric-row">
                  <td class="py-3 ps-0">
                    <span class="d-block fw-bold text-dark small mb-0">Centralized Ledger</span>
                  </td>
                  <td class="pe-0 text-end">
                    <span class="text-muted small">Comprehensive dynamic historical logs complete with granular advanced sorting options and instant spreadsheet export tools.</span>
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="metric-row">
                  <td class="py-3 ps-0">
                    <span class="d-block fw-bold text-dark small mb-0">Security Shell</span>
                  </td>
                  <td class="pe-0 text-end">
                    <span class="text-muted small">Protected session-based authorization walls configured to defend administrative entry terminals from external manipulation.</span>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="card premium-about-card p-4 p-md-5 mb-5">
      <div class="row align-items-center">
        <div class="col-lg-7">
          <h2 class="h6 fw-extrabold text-dark text-uppercase tracking-wider-custom mb-3">Algorithmic Precision Matrix</h2>
          <p class="text-secondary small lh-lg mb-0">
            SAMS processes geometry tracking nodes entirely within your native workstation environment. Upon loading an active hardware camera viewport, the alignment pipeline extracts 68 unique baseline spatial landmarks. These structures map into a dense 128-float coordinate array, cross-checking verification tolerance ratings using standard mathematical Euclidean calculations.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-light p-3 rounded-3 mt-3 border font-monospace text-dark text-center" style="font-size:0.82rem;">
            $$\text{Euclidean Distance} = \sqrt{\sum_{i=1}^{128} (x_i - y_i)^2} \le 0.60$$
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-5 mt-4 mt-lg-0">
          <div class="p-4 rounded-4 border bg-light h-100">
            <h6 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-2 small d-flex align-items-center gap-2">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-eye text-primary"></i> Anti-Spoofing Liveness Verification
            </h6>
            <p class="text-muted small lh-base mb-0">
              To defend the database matrix against presentation attacks using printed physical photos or static mobile display screens, the core engine measures biometric motion signals. By tracking structural eye state movements via Eye Aspect Ratio formulas, the portal logs records only for active, physically present individuals.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card premium-about-card p-4 p-md-5">
      <div class="mb-4">
        <h2 class="h6 fw-extrabold text-dark text-uppercase tracking-wider-custom m-0">SAMS Continuous Engineering Roadmap</h2>
        <small class="text-muted">Targeted enhancement scopes for subsequent system updates</small>
      </div>
      
      <div class="row g-4">
        <div class="col-md-3">
          <div class="roadmap-node">
            <div class="roadmap-icon-wrap">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-arrows-left-right-to-line"></i>
            </div>
            <h6 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-1 small">Toggle Session Logic</h6>
            <p class="text-muted m-0" style="font-size: 0.78rem; line-height: 1.5;">Changes structural logging parameters dynamically to handle both student arrival check-ins and departure checkout lifecycles.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="col-md-3">
          <div class="roadmap-node">
            <div class="roadmap-icon-wrap">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-users-viewfinder"></i>
            </div>
            <h6 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-1 small">Multi-Target Acquisition</h6>
            <p class="text-muted m-0" style="font-size: 0.78rem; line-height: 1.5;">Scales pipeline ingestion capabilities to scan, calibrate, and record multiple simultaneous student facial frames inside a single camera viewport.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="col-md-3">
          <div class="roadmap-node">
            <div class="roadmap-icon-wrap">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-cloud-arrow-up"></i>
            </div>
            <h6 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-1 small">Cloud Sync Ecosystems</h6>
            <p class="text-muted m-0" style="font-size: 0.78rem; line-height: 1.5;">Extends the local host container deployment baseline out into managed distributed clouds paired with automated communication alert relays.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="col-md-3">
          <div class="roadmap-node">
            <div class="roadmap-icon-wrap">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-chart-pie"></i>
            </div>
            <h6 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-1 small">Long-Term Analytics</h6>
            <p class="text-muted m-0" style="font-size: 0.78rem; line-height: 1.5;">Integrates deep administrative trend metrics tools equipped with interactive graphic panels to evaluate institutional engagement profiles.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </main>

  <%- include("partials/footer") %>

</body>
</html>